data.description: Welcome to this beautiful home that is in a great location. This 3 bedroom 2 bath home sits on a oversized corner lot, featuring a formal dinning, formal sitting or office area, large kitchen overlooking the family room with French doors, Luxury plank flooring throughout the whole home. The spacious owners bedroom has room for all your furniture and more, Large owners bathroom has double sinks, oversized vanity, soaking tub, and a walk in closet. Home is in the highly desirable Crystal Springs area on an oversized fully fenced corner lot, and has enough room in the back yard for all the activities, fun, or toys you could want, . Don't let this one pass you by call for your showing today! Ask about the VA assumable mortgage
